  ('dietitian-moex-05002', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-111-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '阿茲海默症（Alzheimer''sdementia）的4As對應於營養上的影響，下列敘述何者正確？', '["Amnesia：無法記得吃過什麼，但很信任照顧者", "Aphasia：無法說出吃過什麼", "Apraxia：因身體肌肉及協調問題導致無法順利的吃、咀嚼、吞嚥", "Agnosia：忘記食物的名稱而不敢吃，導致營養不良"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "12def22d8e48", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fb471fe128ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-05003', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-111-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '新生兒及幼兒相關之代謝遺傳疾病與飲食治療原則，下列何者錯誤？', '["Ureacycledisorders限制蛋白質飲食", "GlycogenstoragediseasetypeI限制醣類飲食", "Galactosemia 限制乳製品", "Fattyacidoxidationdisorders低脂（≦30% 熱量）或限制脂肪飲食"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "12def22d8e48", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fb471fe128ad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
